      <description>&lt;h2 id="changes"&gt;Changes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FIX &lt;a href="https://github.com/padrino/padrino-framework/pull/2177" title="#2177"&gt;#2177&lt;/a&gt; regexp routes and trailing slashes (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pdlug" title="pdlug"&gt;pdlug&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
