&lt;li&gt;FIX &lt;a href="https://github.com/padrino/padrino-framework/pull/2185" title="#2185"&gt;#2185&lt;/a&gt; self.authenticate method in mongoid.rb.tt (&lt;a href="https://github.com/LarryFransson" title="LarryFransson"&gt;LarryFransson&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FIX &lt;a href="https://github.com/padrino/padrino-framework/pull/2179" title="#2179"&gt;#2179&lt;/a&gt; Deprecate safe_level of &lt;code&gt;ERB.new&lt;/code&gt; in Ruby 2.6 (&lt;a href="https://github.com/koic" title="koic"&gt;koic&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
